i was so bored in math that i decided to write a note to patrick, so i did, and in line, joe ripped it! i was mad, at the end of the day, i was all to patrick "i have a note for you" he then asked "who's it from?" i told him "me" hes all "well give it to me" i put it in my pocket and said "i dont want to anymore" hes all "come on give it to me" i'm all "no" then i'm all "fine i will" so i gave it to him and then ran out the door, the note said that its true that i liked him and told him wat happened after i got home yesterday (the fight w/ my parents) and it also said to aim me and stuff, so yeah i'm totally nervouse!  but hes so sweet so i dont expect anything bad

i asked patrick, cause brittney said that she was gonna tell him that i liked him, and so i asked patrick "did brittany tell you any thing unusual?" he said "that you liked me" and i was all "omg! i'm gonna kill her!" and hes all "ha! she never told me that! you DO like me! i got u bad!" i was all "no i dont like u" and it went back and forth for a while until i was walking home and said "maybe i do but if i did i wouldn't tell you" then i just ran off.
Well last weekend i went to the beach... here are 2 pics... the other pics are real dumb. so yeah

WOW! such a long time since i have updated! almost a full month! ok so basicly i've been workin on my site & doing requests, and blah blah blah...

But.

i'm havin a great time w/ patrick, well sorta, i'm kinda like stalking him, & blaming it on my friend, if u see him, u would kno y the heck i'm stalking him! hes so fine! anyways, a major thing that happened was that last friday: 

he always plays basketball during lunch so after i eat me & my friend marina go to the gym, well i dunno why but we had to be in the up-stairs gym cause the main gym was closed, so after lunch was over he grabbed his binder and went down stairs so we were going out the door too when i saw his sweater on the floor i grabed it and marina was all "ewww but it down" i'm all "noway! this is patrick's and i'm gonna give it to him" and so i was gonna give it to him when it feel from my hands and landed on the stair case, well there was like 100 people behind us so i couldn't go back i felt bad during 4th, 5th, and 6th period till finally it was 3:15 and skol was o-u-t so i was at my friends locker (which his locker s rite next 2 hers; i wonder y i was there *thinx* anyclays,) my friend is all "when did u get ur sweater back?" (i told her about wat happened) he said, "i got it before i went to 4th period, but people were stepping on it, 'cause someone threw it on the starie case" i started laughing he thought my friend did it he pointed at her and said "YOU!" and i was still laughing and then he said "YOU IT WAS YOU IMAN!!!!" (iman is my real name pro-nounced E-man) and he pushed my backpack, then left, i felt real bad but it was so funny! and so i walk home and my friend rides the bus, so i was walking out w/ her 2 her bus and i saw patrick walking out with his bike, i yelled "sorri patrick!" he said something but i couldn't hear wat it wuz, so yeah that was long a detailed! i'm gonna go now! later!

~Amy

Since Patrick knows i like him, he's been avoiding me a little to much. Its very annoying to me, honestly. I looked 4 him at lunch but he wasn't anywhere 2 b found, not even the gym. *crys* Finally i saw him in the health office, he was hurt, i used one of my ELA bathroom passes and kept walking back & forth trying to see his beautiful eyes. I did. After school the Yearbook teacher asked me to stay after to talk 2 her about the yearbook and he was behind me. OMC! i was freaken out after i saw him. I smiled and he ignored. I asked Michelle to tell Patrick that i didn't like him, i dunno if she told him or not though. 

Anyclays, i just got done watching TRL that my mom taped for me. Clay is soooooooooooooo funny. Lucky Kelly. The Way video clip is cute. while i was watching it i saw me and patrick... i dunno y, but he's always on my mind, hey! thats a grate song eh?

Today i went to ACMA and i was a shodow to my old friends, blake and adam. It was coolio. i guess, i tried going back to Brown 2 see patrick but my mom said no, (i told her i was going cause i needed to get my HW)

NO! and i was so nervouse for 3 periods! arg... oh well, michelle HELP ME GIRL! EDIT: So i heard patrick likes some1 in his art class... i'm so DEPRESSED!

2day was alrite i gave a note to patrick sayin that i think hes cute and i like him and blah blah blah, i signed it "me" i wont tell him its REALLY me till l8r...

Off Topic Of Patrick:

Today was fab! *sigh* ha! ok so yesterday i told patrick that there is this girl who likes him (which is me) and yeah, today he helped me open my jammed locker, i must say he is mighty strong! ha! anyclays, i was feeling so wonderful, i play basketball with marina she is kinda um... trying 2 b funny, i wish she would stop. Anyclays, it was the end of skol, i was going to my locker and he tried to trip me! ahhhh! i was gonna fall, but i didn't i looked back at him and he smiled, i got my stuff quick and went to his locker. i hit his head (i'm not washing my right hand!) and he said "oww" the beauty of how he says it makes me wanna thud. and i was about to. i asked him why he tryed to tip me and he said "'cause u wont tell me who likes me" i told him that she (me) wouldn't tell him till the end of the year or b4 spring brake... Thats when i need ur help! post me a comment tellin me what i should do... i'm thinkin of walkin with him home sometime and i might tell him then. i dunno

Yes Yes, Boredome is a great thing, especially when you are thinking of the past *sigh* I keep on thinking of the guy who i had that after skol 'incident' with (muh friends kno what i'm sayin) well his name is patrick, and i totally like him now. crazy or what? Reality: Patrick

I'm just hoping that i'll get to talk to him twm. *wishes*
